312    /**
313    * A general class for plotting data in the form of (x, y) pairs. This plot can
314    * use data from any class that implements the {@link XYDataset} interface.
315    * <P>
316    * <code>XYPlot</code> makes use of an {@link XYItemRenderer} to draw each point
317    * on the plot. By using different renderers, various chart types can be
318    * produced.
319    * <p>
320    * The {@link ChartFactory} class contains static methods for
321    * creating pre-configured charts.
322    */
